+ *  @dev: Device pointer.
+ *  @rq: An IOCTL specefic structure, that can contain a pointer to
+ *  a proprietary structure used to pass information to the driver.
+ *  @cmd: IOCTL command
+ *  Description:
+ *  Currently it supports the phy_mii_ioctl(...) and HW time stamping.
